  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/5538486c101fa8f63fe277b959df5152.poster.avif?t=1753451898\" width=600 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/5538486c101fa8f63fe277b959df5152.webm?t=1753451898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/5538486c101fa8f63fe277b959df5152.mp4?t=1753451898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discover the origins of I Am Your President story by playing as a protagonist’s predecessor!<br><br><strong>I Am Your President: Prologue</strong> is a free game that includes features available in the full version. Play this narrative strategy simulator in order to experience an engaging story with branching dialogues and different endings. Use the right strategy to win the election and if you fail, you can always get a second chance! <br><br>Simply put, become the President of the United States and decide on the fate of the seven billion people by making some difficult choices. Can you rise to the challenge?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In order to make it work, you will have to</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/6e8fafc88577f93cf3c866b028e33b7e.webp?t=1753451898\" width=23 height=25 /></span> Make yourself comfortable in the Oval Office and let the story unfold.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/6e8fafc88577f93cf3c866b028e33b7e.webp?t=1753451898\" width=23 height=25 /></span> Select dialogue options that suit you best and watch them affect the statistics. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/6e8fafc88577f93cf3c866b028e33b7e.webp?t=1753451898\" width=23 height=25 /></span> Wisely choose your advisors and cabinet members. Hire and fire on a daily basis.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/6e8fafc88577f93cf3c866b028e33b7e.webp?t=1753451898\" width=23 height=25 /></span> Decide upon the way of ruling and embrace consequences – your decisions matter!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/6e8fafc88577f93cf3c866b028e33b7e.webp?t=1753451898\" width=23 height=25 /></span> React to the events on the world map and choose the best way to resolve the conflict. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/6e8fafc88577f93cf3c866b028e33b7e.webp?t=1753451898\" width=23 height=25 /></span> Use social media and read the news – maybe this time they wrote something nice?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/6e8fafc88577f93cf3c866b028e33b7e.webp?t=1753451898\" width=23 height=25 /></span> Choose your path and replay the game to see other outcomes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1201330/extras/6e8fafc88577f93cf3c866b028e33b7e.webp?t=1753451898\" width=23 height=25 /></span> Provide sustainable development, or simply watch your country fall into chaos.",
